### Admin Login (for creating invitations)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "adminpassword"
}

###

### Create an Invitation (Requires Admin/SuperAdmin token)
# Replace {{admin_jwt_token}} with the token obtained from the Admin Login request
POST http://localhost:3000/invitations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt_token}}

{
  "email": "newemployee@example.com",
  "role": "employee"
}

###

### Accept an Invitation (Public endpoint)
# Replace {{invitation_token}} with the token received from the Create Invitation response
POST http://localhost:3000/invitations/accept
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-1234-567890abcdef",
  "password": "newsecurepassword"
}

###

### Get all vacations
GET http://localhost:3000/vacations
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all health status
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Create a new vacation
POST http://localhost:3000/vacations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": "123",
  "startDate": "2026-01-20",
  "endDate": "2026-01-25",
  "type": "PAID"
}

###

### Get vacation by ID (replace {id} with real UUID)
GET http://localhost:3000/vacations/20744c41-563e-43ab-9ccc-ad1100429955
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update vacation status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/vacations/20744c41-563e-43ab-9ccc-ad1100429955/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

###

### Delete vacation
DELETE http://localhost:3000/vacations/20744c41-563e-43ab-9ccc-ad1100429955
Content-Type: application/json

